name: U.S. Weekly Leading Index
description: Has a moderate lead over cyclical turns in U.S. economic activity. Historical data begins in 1967.

name: U.S. Monthly Coincident Index
description: Coincides with U.S. economic cycles. Historical data begins in 1919.

name: U.S. Monthly Lagging Index
description: Lags cyclical turns in U.S. economic activity. Historical data begins in 1948.
